<doc id="411966" wikidata="Q11274538" url="?curid=411966" title="Hong He (disambiguation)">
<text>Hong He or Honghe (Chinese:  ,  ,  &quot;Hóng Hé&quot;,  &quot;Red River&quot;) typically refers to the Red River of southern China and northern Vietnam.

