* &quot;Red River&quot;, a 2008 Chinese film
*Honghe Hani and Yi Autonomous Prefecture (, &quot;Hónghé Hānízú–Yízú Zìzhìzhōu; Hani: &quot;Haoqhoqxeif) in Yunnan, China

